             were indicted for <rs id="t18290409-200-off1137" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290409-200-off1137" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290409-200-off1137" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290409-200-cd1138" type="crimeDate">4th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-200-off1137 t18290409-200-cd1138"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290409-200-victim1927" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Howle
                        <interp inst="t18290409-200-victim1927" type="surname" value="Howle"></interp>
